us lot, but between these many classic tales of spouses pulling fast ones on each other or selfless tales of true love or steadfastness or tales of corruption, greed, and confidence games, I'm tempted to just throw in the hat and say this guy has it ALL.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eI know it ain't true. I've read enough Italians from more than a millennia prior to put paid to that idea. But STILL. This is entertaining as hell. And I thought Chaucer was a RIOT, too.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIt just goes to show... never judge a book by its cover. You might be losing out on some GREAT comedy.","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4213258?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"traditional-fiction","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4213258?shelf=traditional-fiction"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"humor","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4213258?shelf=humor"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"satire","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4213258?shelf=satire"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"romance","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4213258?shelf=romance"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"2019-shelf","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4213258?shelf=2019-shelf"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2438973871"},"likeCount":82,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":11,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:2294090":{"id":2294090,"__typename":"User","legacyId":2294090,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1547440402i/2294090._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":1556,"viewableName":"Darwin8u","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodr