ntertaining. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100 stories told during the the summer of 1348 as the Black Death is ravaging Florence (and Europe). Ten aristocratic youths take to the country to escape the death, stink and bodies of the City and to hang out and amuse themselves on stories of love and adventure and sex and trickery. Bad priests, evil princes, saints, sinners, and various twists and turns paints a detailed picture of Italy from over 660 years ago that seems just as modern and funky as today. Things have certainly changed, but lords and ladies it is incredible just how many things have stayed the same.","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/2294090?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"aere-perennius","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/2294090?shelf=aere-perennius"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"2014","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/2294090?shelf=2014"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/208682456"},"likeCount":79,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":12,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.w-7xFpuuPGPNCmOAIsIE3w":{"id":"kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.w-7xFpuuPGPNCmOAIsIE3w","__typename":"Work","legacyId":1320474,"bestBook":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.FK2Pq5q7kZ9N0n8cOCOIyQ"},"details":{"__typename":"WorkDetails","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/1320474-il-decamerone","shelvesUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/shelves/1320474-il-decamerone","publicationTime":-19596787200000,"originalTitle":"Il Decamerone","awardsWon":[{"__typename":"Award","name":"Премія імені Максима Рильського","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/28835","awardedAt":568022400000,"category":"","hasWon":true},{"__typename":"Award","name":"PEN Center USA Literary Award","webUrl":"https://www.goo